{"tid":1653821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日將軍澳醫院醫護人員靜坐，聲援被無理拘捕醫生 大部分帶口罩","createTime":"2019-10-14T09:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T03:20:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f37e5212207ce381154fe62ec7bd183f36bed381","tid":1653821,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azO36Em.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazO36Em.png&h=f023ccfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近百名戴上黑口罩的醫護人員，在將軍澳醫院主座大樓地下靜坐。部分人胸口前繫上黑絲帶，聲援周日在將軍澳商場被捕的將軍澳外科醫生。<br />\n<br />\n現場人士展示「聲援被捕醫生、抗議警方濫捕」及「警察黑心、醫護良心」等標語。除了醫護人員，亦有數名市民自發加入。<br />\n<br />\n有參與集會的醫護人員表示，當時該名同事無明顯衝擊行為，認為警方拘捕不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/將軍澳醫院醫護人員靜坐聲援周日被捕醫生-062034951.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%9D%9C%E5%9D%90%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-062034951.html&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=ddf791dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/將軍澳醫院醫護人員靜坐聲援周日被捕醫生-062034951.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033e18c34199a1c42991757dcd35e808c99da32a","tid":1653821,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"10.14 人權民主法集氣大會🇺🇸<br />\n時間：晚上七點正<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園"},{"pid":"1bb5b658852f62c9a5e05b13b5477784f1edddf9","tid":1653821,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03af2e67ae69f1b2c152e1a8d58b4ae2a40a0f94","tid":1653821,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:25:22.000Z